    +main-title( "Font Style" )

    +intro-text
        :marked
            It's possible to modify the style of text by
            using the `font-style` css classes shown below.

    :marked
        The values of `normal` and `italic` are really the
        only necessary ones, as most web fonts do not have an
        `oblique` typeface and it can be simluated by adding
        [`fw-b` from the font-weights](./font-weight.html) class list.

        _It's also possible to add `oblique` yourself [by customising
        the styles map](#customising)._

